    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">World ID expands its &#8216;proof of human&#8217; vision for the AI era</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Identity management is a critical concern for any enterprise, and it’s becoming ever more complex and convoluted with the advent of AI agents.
World ID is taking a unique (and to some, controversial) approach to this challenge by building a ‘digital proof of human’ ecosystem for the internet.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/17/world-id-expands-its-proof-of-human-vision-for-the-ai-era/"  >(Computer World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
