    <h3 itemprop="headline">Samsung Messages ending? What Android owners must know</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Samsung is phasing out Samsung Messages by July 2026 in the U.S. and pushing Google Messages, but scam texts are targeting confused Galaxy phone owners.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/11/samsung-messages-ending-android-owners-must-know/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
