    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Younger adult colon cancer deaths are concentrated in people with less education, study says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A new study finds the worrisome rise in colorectal cancer deaths among younger adults is concentrated in people with less education.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/16/younger-adult-colon-cancer-deaths-are-concentrated-in-people-with-less-education-study-says/"  >(Mike Stobbe, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
