    <h3 itemprop="headline">Utah justice allegedly sent &#8216;inappropriate&#8217; texts to lawyer in key redistricting case, officials launch probe</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Utah officials ordered a probe into Supreme Court Justice Diana Hagen over alleged ties to an attorney involved in a key redistricting case ruling.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/17/utah-leaders-launch-probe-supreme-court-justice-over-alleged-relationship-redistricting-lawyer/"  >(Fox News)</a>
