    <h3 itemprop="headline">White House chief of staff meets with Anthropic CEO over its new AI technology</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      White House chief of staff Susie Wiles has met with Anthropic CEO Dario Amodei to discuss the company's new AI model, Mythos.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/17/white-house-chief-of-staff-to-meet-with-anthropic-ceo-over-its-new-ai-technology/"  >(Josh Boak And Matt O'Brien, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
