    <h3 itemprop="headline">Former Wisconsin man sentenced to 20 months in federal prison for illegal campaign contributions</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A federal judge has sentenced a former Wisconsin man to 20 months in prison for making campaign contributions after renouncing his U.S. citizenship.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/17/former-wisconsin-man-sentenced-to-20-months-in-federal-prison-for-illegal-campaign-contributions/"  >(Todd Richmond, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
