</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 17 Apr 2026 21:16:17 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 17 Apr 2026 21:16:17 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Texas Tribune, Kayla Guo, KPRC 2">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/04/17/three-dozen-texas-democrats-urge-kendall-scudder-not-to-seek-reelection-as-state-party-chair.webp" alt="Three dozen Texas Democrats urge Kendall Scudder not to seek reelection as state party chair" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Three dozen Texas Democrats urge Kendall Scudder not to seek reelection as state party chair</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      In an open letter, former staffers and other insiders said the state party has fallen short on strategy and failed to act with urgency under Scudder’s leadership.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/17/three-dozen-texas-democrats-urge-kendall-scudder-not-to-seek-reelection-as-state-party-chair/"  >(Texas Tribune, Kayla Guo, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 17 Apr 2026 19:57:10 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 17 Apr 2026 19:57:10 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Erica Zurek, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/04/17/minnesota-up-against-the-clock-on-medicaid-changes.webp" alt="Minnesota up against the clock on Medicaid changes" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Minnesota up against the clock on Medicaid changes</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Democrats and Republicans in the Minnesota Legislature say they need to either pass legislation or update existing rules soon to ensure that state programs comply with new requirements from the federal government.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/17/minnesota-up-against-the-clock-on-medicaid-changes/"  >(Erica Zurek, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
